[&SelectRelation relation-field="OPS01",ref="scope"]

** All fields free text, but labels need changing for essential fields, and some need hiding for private contacts
[&If scope.EN06="COMM"]    *** Commercial OPS
   [&Field code="OPS08",attribute="label",value="Main Contact"] ** @Contact COMM
   [&Field code="OPS09",attribute="label",value="Direct Dial"]
