   [&Field code="OPS12",attribute="visible",value="No"] ** Private Daytime
   [&Field code="OPS07",attribute="visible",value="No"] ** Private Mobile
   
   [&Field code="OPS13",attribute="visible",value="No"] ** Private contact: Evening
   [&Field code="OPS14",attribute="visible",value="No"] ** Private contact: Mobile
   [&Field code="OPS15",attribute="visible",value="No"] ** Private Contact: Fax
[&Else]                        *** Private OPS
   [&Field code="OPS08",attribute="label",value="Contact"] ** @Contact PRIV
   [&Field code="OPS09",attribute="label",value="Daytime"]
   [&Field code="OPS04",attribute="script",value=" "]

   [&Field code="OPS02",attribute="visible",value="no"] ** Commercial name pointer
