   [&Field code="OPS11",attribute="visible",value="Yes"] ** Private Address
   [&Field code="OPS12",attribute="visible",value="Yes"] ** Private Daytime
   [&Field code="OPS07",attribute="visible",value="Yes"] ** Private Mobile
   
   [&Field code="OPS13",attribute="visible",value="Yes"] ** Evening
   [&Field code="OPS14",attribute="visible",value="Yes"] ** Mobile
   [&Field code="OPS15",attribute="visible",value="Yes"] ** Fax
[&EndIf]


